# Glossary

Canonical vocabulary for {{ project_name }}. Entries may declare exact strings
that count as usage and rejected synonyms that should not appear in docs.

No terms yet. Add your first term as a level-2 heading; the indented block
below shows the shape (it is an example, not a live entry):

    ## Pipeline

    match: ["Pipeline"]
    forbidden_synonyms: ["Workflow"]
    case_sensitive: true

    _One- or two-sentence definition._

## Anti-glossary

Synonyms we explicitly reject in this codebase. New contributors otherwise reintroduce them.

- _Don't say `Workflow`; we call it `Pipeline`._
